**Core Message**

Our project is not a “free-form autonomous agent” in the usual LangChain/LangGraph sense. It is a **single orchestrator with controlled tools**, where the backend first uses deterministic rules to decide what AWS capability is needed, falls back to a compact LLM planner only when the route is ambiguous, fetches **live AWS data as the source of truth**, and then uses the LLM mainly to **compose a good answer**. The center of that design is in [chat_service.py](c:/Users/91997/proj1test/backend/app/services/chat_service.py#L144), [tool_catalog.py](c:/Users/91997/proj1test/backend/app/chat/tool_catalog.py#L20), and [aws_service.py](c:/Users/91997/proj1test/backend/app/services/aws_service.py#L36).

